, in 2014, had a population density of 13.25 people per square kilometer. The most recent census states the population stands at 15,103<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.citypopulation.de/en/angola/communes/admin/cuanza_norte/05202__luinga/|title=Luinga (Commune, Angola) - Population Statistics, Charts, Map and Location|website=www.citypopulation.de|access-date=2020-04-16}}</ref> \n\n== See also ==\n\n* [[Communes of Angola]]\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n\n{{Cuanza Norte Province}}\n\n[[Category:Populated places in Cuanza Norte Province]]\n[[Category:Communes in Cuanza Norte Province]]\n\n\n{{Angola-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n<!--See the Table at Infobox Settlement for all fields and descriptions of usage-->\n<!-- Basic info  ---------------->| name                            = Luinga\n| native_name                     = \n| other_name                      = \n| settlement_type                 = [[commune]]\n| image_skyline                   = \n| imagesize                       = \n| image_caption                   = \n| image_flag                      = \n| flag_size                       = \n| image_seal                      = \n| seal_size                       = \n| image_shield                    = \n| shield_size                     = \n| nickname                        = \n| motto                           = \n| image_map                       = \n| mapsize                         = \n| map_caption                     = \n| pushpin_map                     = Angola\n| pushpin_label_position          = right\n| pushpin_mapsize                 = 300\n| pushpin_map_caption             = Location in Angola\n| coordinates                     = \n| subdivision_type                = Country\n| subdivision_name                = {{flag|Angola}}\n| subdivision_type1               = [[Provinces of Angola|Province]]\n| subdivision_type2               = \n| subdivision_type3               = \n| subdivision_name1               = [[Cuanza Norte Pr